Module Mal4J

Package com.kttdevelopment.mal4j.anime.property

Contains Anime properties.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnimePreviewRetrievable
    Indicates that an Anime preview can be retrieved from the object.
    AnimeRetrievable
    Indicates that an Anime can be retrieved from the object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimeStatistics
    Represents an Anime's statistics.
    Broadcast
    Represents the broadcast time of an Anime.
    EndingTheme
    Represents an Anime ending.
    OpeningTheme
    Represents an Anime opening.
    StartSeason
    Represents the start season for an Anime.
    Studio
    Represents an Anime studio.
    Theme
    Represents an Anime op/ed.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AnimeAirStatus
    Represents an Anime's airing status.
    AnimeRankingType
    Represents the Anime ranking type.
    AnimeRating
    Represents the Anime's TV viewing rating (ex: pg13).
    AnimeSeasonSort
    Represents how to sort the Anime season query.
    AnimeSort
    Represents how to sort the Anime search query.
    AnimeSource
    Represents the source material for an Anime.
    AnimeStatus
    Represents an Anime's status on a users Anime list.
    AnimeType
    Represents the type of media that the Anime is.
    RewatchValue
    Represents a Anime listings rewatch value.
